<lb n="0041a18"/><head type="no">No. 1210</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0041a19"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0041014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】仁平二年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本，【丙】保安三年寫東寺三密藏本，降＋（伏）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0041014"><lem>降</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">降伏</rdg></app><note n="0041014" place="foot" type="rest">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】仁平二年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】平安時代寫仁和寺藏本，【丙】保安三年寫東寺三密藏本</note>三世忿怒<note n="0041015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔明〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041015"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>王念誦儀<note n="0041016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＋（別儀軌）細註【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0041016"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">軌<note place="inline">別儀軌</note></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0041a20"/>
<lb n="0041a21"/><byline type="Translator">特進試鴻臚<note n="0041017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鄉＝卿【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041017"><lem>鄉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">卿</rdg></app>大興
<lb n="0041a22"/>善寺三藏沙門大廣智
<lb n="0041a23"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0041a24"/><p>爾時諸佛菩薩一切賢聖現世間。利益一切
<lb n="0041a25"/>有情。時為非順正法<note n="0041018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔相〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041018"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。損壞國土眾生魔
<lb n="0041a26"/>等。阿&CB00434;普賢大弘誓甚深故示現忿怒形相。
<lb n="0041a27"/>白<note n="0041019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0041019"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>言。我在真言。於世間甚所希有。諸如
<lb n="0041a28"/>來被聽宣說真言。我等當守護諸佛教法饒
<lb n="0041a29"/>益一切有情。爾時<app type="＊" source="0041019"><lem>佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>告言。善哉善哉忿怒
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1210.0041b" n="0041b"/>
<lb n="0041b01"/>王。汝聽說降伏真言。則時示現四面八臂極
<lb n="0041b02"/><note n="0041020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝黑【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041020"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">黑</rdg></app>大<note n="0041021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忿＝威【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041021"><lem>忿</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">威</rdg></app>怒形相。說真言句頌。真言曰</p>
<lb n="0041b03"/><p type="dharani">唵蘇<note place="inline">蘇<note n="0041022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吽＝乎【乙】</note><app n="0041022"><lem>吽</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">乎</rdg></app>反</note>婆&CB00135;蘇婆吽<note place="inline">短呼<note n="0041023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">下同＝之同下【甲】，同下【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0041023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">下同＝之同下【甲】，＝同下【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041023"><lem>下同</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">之同下</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">同下</rdg></app></note>&CB00617;哩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶拏<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0041b04"/>合</note>&CB00617;哩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶拏<note place="inline">二合</note>吽&CB00617;哩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶拏<note place="inline">二合</note>波耶
<lb n="0041b05"/>吽阿那野斛<note n="0041024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【乙】</note><app n="0041024"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>婆<note n="0041025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00344;＝哦【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041025"><lem>&CB00344;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">哦</rdg></app>&CB01227;&CB00085;日<note n="0041026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">羅＝囉【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0041026"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">囉</rdg></app><note n="0041027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔二合〕－【乙】</note><app n="0041027"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吽<note n="0041028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01215;＝泮【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041028"><lem>&CB01215;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">泮</rdg></app>
<lb n="0041b06"/>吒</p>
<lb n="0041b07"/><p><note n="0041029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔爾時〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0041029"><lem>爾時</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>普賢大士等。說此真言時。三千大千世
<lb n="0041b08"/>界六種震動。所有天魔鬼界。於眾生生損害
<lb n="0041b09"/>者。皆悉恐怖非得安樂。各走集白忿怒尊言。
<lb n="0041b10"/>唯願愍念令我無恐懼。爾時忿怒王。皆令得
<lb n="0041b11"/>安穩。則尚右足下踏大自在魔王。左足下踏
<lb n="0041b12"/>魔婦人。於國土有情。皆令得快樂。誦此真
<lb n="0041b13"/>言一遍。則無量無邊魔界。各苦惱熱病故。於
<lb n="0041b14"/>行者生障礙<note n="0041030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者無得＝無【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041030"><lem>者無得</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>便者。變成<note n="0041031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行者〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0041031"><lem>行者</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>僕從
<lb n="0041b15"/>乃到妨難。行者　<note n="0041032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（隨）＋宜【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041032"><lem>宜</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">隨宜</rdg></app>須護三業內外。此亦
<lb n="0041b16"/><note n="0041033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可辟＝避【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041033"><lem>可辟</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">避</rdg></app>除結界印身五處。作契儀則。可見金剛
<lb n="0041b17"/>頂瑜伽教中。更不<note n="0041034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翻＝新【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041034"><lem>翻</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">新</rdg></app>譯。復不須作諸契法
<lb n="0041b18"/>印。但威驗皆在此真言。亦無有別&CB00057;。若欲修
<lb n="0041b19"/>此真言者面東。像前忿怒<note n="0041035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝嗔【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041035"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">嗔</rdg></app>。想我身則<note n="0041036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041036"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0041b20"/>不異本尊威怒王。則<note n="0041037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔淨〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041037"><lem>淨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三業。所<note n="0041038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＝誦【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0041038"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">誦</rdg></app>吽字三
<lb n="0041b21"/>遍。亦安法界。則二手堅固縛捧額上。左右三
<lb n="0041b22"/>轉亦成辟除結界。次至心合掌。禮拜忿怒尊
<lb n="0041b23"/>諸聖眾</p>
<lb n="0041b24"/><p>若欲降伏<note n="0041039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一切〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041039"><lem>一切</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>惡人。作三角爐。壇向南。取
<lb n="0041b25"/>惡木一遍一燒。滿三百二十四遍。惡人自降
<lb n="0041b26"/>伏生歸依</p>
<lb n="0041b27"/><p>又欲令惡人<note n="0041040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病疾＝疾病【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041040"><lem>病疾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">疾病</rdg></app>者。作調伏壇誦根本真言。
<lb n="0041b28"/><note n="0041041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041041"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>千八十遍。燒赤黑二種芥子。一千八十粒
<lb n="0041b29"/>一遍一燒。真言句中誦姓名。則<note n="0041042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝沈【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041042"><lem>洗</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">沈</rdg></app>長病而無
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1210.0041c" n="0041c"/>
<lb n="0041c01"/>死滅</p>
<lb n="0041c02"/><p>若欲除病者。作息災壇向東。燒白米一千粒
<lb n="0041c03"/>一&CB00057;一燒真言句中。安除病<note n="0041043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宇＝字【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041043"><lem>宇</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">字</rdg></app>則息病。歸伏
<lb n="0041c04"/>佛法。無有異心如<note n="0041044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝比【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041044"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">比</rdg></app>枝木</p>
<lb n="0041c05"/><p>若欲頓滅惡人。爐中安惡人<note n="0041045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姓＝性【甲】</note><app n="0041045"><lem>姓</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">性</rdg></app>名形。以惡心
<lb n="0041c06"/>誦&CB00057;<note n="0041046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【乙】＊</note><app n="0041046"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>百八遍。以砂打惡人燒之。則死。若
<lb n="0041c07"/>欲急甦。對忿怒王。以慈<note n="0041047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔悲〕－【乙】</note><app n="0041047"><lem>悲</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>心誦一百八遍。
<lb n="0041c08"/>不過時甦<note n="0041048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝亦【乙】</note><app n="0041048"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">亦</rdg></app>無損壞</p>
<lb n="0041c09"/><p>若欲勝軍陣者。取<note n="0041049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香花＝花香【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041049"><lem>香花</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">花香</rdg></app>木一百八枚。誦真言
<lb n="0041c10"/>燒之。即雖魔敵軍即時得勝。亦須五穀五香。
<lb n="0041c11"/>若無者隨在。莫惱<note n="0041050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不得〕－&M062485;【原】，〔不〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041050"><lem><sic corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">不得</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0041c12"/><p>若欲入山林不遭惡禽獸毒虫者。二手掌內
<lb n="0041c13"/>把隨節之石&CB00057;二七遍。打投行道前。雖禽獸
<lb n="0041c14"/>毒虫皆降伏。敢無有害損心</p>
<lb n="0041c15"/><p>若欲被敬愛國王大臣者。作敬愛壇爐燒菊
<lb n="0041c16"/>根<app type="＊" source="0041046"><lem>一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>百八枚。一&CB00057;一燒<note n="0041051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0041051"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>則敬愛自來</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1210.0042a" n="0042a"/>
<lb n="0042a01"/><p>若欲濟助重病人者。對像前&CB00057;香水<note n="0042001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【乙】</note><app n="0042001"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>百八
<lb n="0042a02"/>遍。急撮入病者腹懷內。則醒起</p>
<lb n="0042a03"/><p>若欲留癲&CB04229;<note n="0042002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔病〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042002"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>者。取龍水則<note n="0042003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00057;〕－【甲】</note><app n="0042003"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一百八遍。
<lb n="0042a04"/>洗二眼口舌等。自然消滅無有他病</p>
<lb n="0042a05"/><p>若欲縛男女令問顯<note n="0042004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝萬【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042004"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">萬</rdg></app>辭。取柘榴木一丈二
<lb n="0042a06"/>尺加持一萬<note n="0042005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔遍〕－【乙】</note><app n="0042005"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。然<note n="0042006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">後＋（到）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042006"><lem>後</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">後到</rdg></app>別處。以<note n="0042007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枝＝杖【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0042007"><lem>枝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">杖</rdg></app>一&CB00057;一
<lb n="0042a07"/>打。打人二七處。即萬事隨問皆顯語。即想意
<lb n="0042a08"/><note n="0042008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">計＝許【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042008"><lem>計</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">許</rdg></app>被解縛</p>
<lb n="0042a09"/><p><note n="0042009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042009"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>行者修此法時。七七日間。須斷五穀味鹽
<lb n="0042a10"/>一心無餘境滿真言十萬遍。爾時本尊現形。
<lb n="0042a11"/>作大惡怖魔體。試謙行者心。是時慎勿生散
<lb n="0042a12"/>發則法成就</p>
<lb n="0042a13"/><p>爾時忿怒<note n="0042010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝尊【甲】【丙】</note><app n="0042010"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">尊</rdg></app>說<note n="0042011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝是【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042011"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>真言時。一切天<note n="0042012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魔＋（處）【甲】</note><app n="0042012"><lem>魔</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">魔處</rdg></app>惡鬼
<lb n="0042a14"/>等。皆大降伏。而信受歸依佛道。各作將護
<lb n="0042a15"/><note n="0042013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0042013" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">者</sic>行者</p>
<lb n="0042a16"/><p><note n="0042014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＝以【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042014"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>解<note n="0042015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔結〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042015"><lem>結</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>界。禮佛出堂場。<note n="0042016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">任＝作【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042016"><lem>任</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">作</rdg></app>意讀般若<note n="0042017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等之經＝一&M062403;【原】，也【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0042017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">等之經＝一&M062403;【原】，＝也【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042017"><lem>等
<lb n="0042a17"/>之經</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">一</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0042a18"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>降三世<note n="0042018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔忿怒明王念誦〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0042018"><lem>忿怒明王念誦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>儀<note n="0042019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書曰仁平二年六月六日巳時書了，建久三年十二月二十三日奉傳受了，乙本奧書曰快禪阿闍梨受了，丙本奧書曰保安三年三月一日於高野書寫了，同三日高野傳受了</note>軌</jhead></juan></div1>
